author: Kyle Olson, Kyle Olson
title: Michigan Gov. Gretchen Whitmer: 'Lock Arms' to Fight Coronavirus
description: Gov. Gretchen Whitmer (D-MI) used an unfortunate metaphor Friday when she figuratively urged Michiganders to "lock arms" to fight the Wuhan coronavirus pandemic.
content:
Gov. Gretchen Whitmer (D-MI) used an unfortunate metaphor Friday when she figuratively urged Michiganders to “lock arms” to fight the Wuhan coronavirus pandemic.
